---
title: Shrimp, Pear and Farro Salad with Walnuts, Goat Cheese and Maple-Rosemary Sweet Potatoes
description: This bountiful plate is not just another salad. Fresh pears and earthy, maple-rosemary roasted sweet potatoes add a touch of natural sweetness to complement the nutty farro. Goat cheese and toasted walnuts add textures that ensure this abundant salad is a weeknight winner.
